PRODUCT - which product the bug report is about
COMPONENT - which component contains the bug

SUMMARY - short text describing what's the issue, usually used as the name
          of the report
DESCRIPTION - longer text to describe exact problem
VERSION - list of components relevant to the report
STEPS - steps how to reproduce the issue
ACTUAL_RESULT - describe what's wrong (this might be very similar to SUMMARY
                or description
EXPECTED_RESULT - describe shortly what's the expected result
